channel.title: MSN defence and MSN power! ARE YOU STRONG ENOUGH OR CAN YOU BE TOUGH ENOUGH~
channel.description:
Sup guys. I have been working on scripts lately then i decided to make a bot that can kick some ass. 71 people have fallen to this bot. It will not mess up your computer. But it will boot you off your messenger. Now this is what i call a challenge because you can either try for 2 goals
[ul][li]Goal 1 [POWER]: Take out my bot i.e take my bot off his/her messenger.[/li] [li]Goal 2 [DEFENSE]: With stand an attack from my bot (my bot will only use the weakest attack)[/li][/ul]
This is strictly for fun mind you!
the bots address is: hunter-0000@hotmail.com
P.S this bot may have a hotmail account but it does not run off msn.
Goodluck and dont try lying about the outcome because i log and see all.
